1. Hadoop-MDFS  package-name
2. export JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/java-6-openjdk-amd64
3. ant to build hadoop package
4. conf folder- master, slaves , core-site.xml, hdfs-site.xml, mapred-site.xml
5. bin folder , start-all.sh, start-dfs.sh,start-mapred.sh
5. username: hadoop password: hadoop
6. To start all daemons - execute bin/start-all.sh


